<L>__{interior bathroom minutes later}
<A>__{the light comes on... jack walks in, looks in the mirror, determined to collect himself...but somethings not right... he glances around...the bathroom is small and its cluttered with kates razors, loofah, skin creams... ...none of this stuff is his... ...he looks in the mirror again, his face revealing a forlorn sense of displacement... ...he stares at himself until...he starts to lose it... anger, confusion...sadness...finally, he begins breaking down... after a moment, he turns on the water, rinsing his face...}
